@BlackRock_Hackathon_HostAddress = http://localhost:5146

### Transaction Builder
POST {{BlackRock_Hackathon_HostAddress}}/blackrock/challenge/v1/transactions/parse
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "date": "2023-10-12T20:15:30",
        "amount": 250
    },
    {
        "date": "2023-02-28T15:49:20",
        "amount": 375
    },
    {
        "date": "2023-07-01T21:59:00",
        "amount": 620
    },
    {
        "date": "2023-12-17T08:09:45",
        "amount": 480
    }
]

### Transaction Validator
POST {{BlackRock_Hackathon_HostAddress}}/blackrock/challenge/v1/transactions/validator
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

